Maintainer: PVE GPU Manager <pve-gpu@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12)
Standards-Version: 4.5.1

Package: pve-gpu-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: pve-manager (>= 8.0), perl, libpve-common-perl, pciutils, linux-perf, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: nvidia-smi
Description: GPU Manager for Proxmox VE
 Provides discovery, monitoring, and SR-IOV virtual function management
 for discrete GPUs (Intel Flex/ATS-M, Ponte Vecchio, Battlemage; NVIDIA)
 in Proxmox VE. Includes a web UI tab, REST API, and boot persistence.
